On to the meat of my post. (Lean, sleep-deprived meat, but meat none the less. :P) Now, I would consider this favoritism (FAVORITISM BAD!)if Mr(s). Ambiguous Guild-person one day said, &quot;Hey, moderators. Give me a forum, because I'm am Shaft-like mogul! (or Bruce Lee, Stuart Little, or Joe Camel, whatever floats yer boat...)&quot;<br>
