&quot;Hey, moderators. Give me a forum, because I want to support the community (I'll just use that, since that seems to be the invariable theme) by rewarding people from my guild's plat, equipment, etc... pool.&quot;<br>
&quot;Hey, that's pretty cool. Okay, Mr(s). Ambiguous Guild-person.&quot; = Free Advertising! WUWU! + a rare occasion for a guild to have a potentially positive effect upon individuals as well as guilds outside of themselves.<br>
<br>
Ok... now I see nothing wrong with that. If you form a guild and start handing out free stuff for slapping together an interesting limerick, haiku, wtf ever, I have no problem with you getting advertised. In fact, I'll support you. I will tattoo your guilds acronym onto oblivious ogres' exposed asses, ok?<br>
<br>
DO- write a story, <br>
DO- get a FREE (not out of your pocket; you didn't pay for it; you didn't drop a single plat) lewt. Curse my soul for saying that.<br>
DO- continue on your merry little way.<br>
<br>
DON'T babble on with the typographical semblance of guttural sounds.(That goes for everyone, the Bane faction and the anti-Bane faction, lest you say I'm playing favoritism :P) <br>
<br>
